        "Name": "A Cold Wind Blows",
        "Client": "Dame Rondine",
        "Description": "I have received a dire message\r\nfrom some of my merchant friends.\r\nIt seems that they have been set\r\nupon by a Kushala Daora in the\r\nFrost Islands. There isn\u0027t a moment\r\nto lose, we must rescue them at\r\nonce! Come now, let us depart!",
